item.title: Amenities Section
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
The Club

Park Avenue Tower tenants will enjoy an exclusive amenity space on the concourse level of this iconic building. The 20,000 square foot space includes a high-end fitness center with locker room facilities, lounge area, recreation center, conference rooms and a grab-and-go food concept.

item.title: Location Section
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Location

Located at the epicenter of the Plaza District and blocks from the northern entrance to Grand Central Terminal, Park Avenue Tower features unrivaled amenities with outstanding accessibility. The property is surrounded by world-class retail, superior hotels, residential buildings, and only a short walk to Central Park. Additionally, the area is serviced by multiple subway lines including the nearby N/R, E/M and 4/5/6.

Workspace

This added benefit allows for more natural light and spectacular views of Central Park and the New York skyline. item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!
